    {
      "fields": {
        "remarks": "<format type=\"text/markdown\"><![CDATA[\n## Remarks\n\n`SKColorspaceTransferFnCicp` enumerates the transfer function (gamma / EOTF)\nidentifiers defined by the CICP standard (ITU-T H.273 / ISO 23091-2). Use\nthese values with <xref:SkiaSharp.SKColorSpace.CreateCicp*> to create a color\nspace that matches a specific video or imaging standard.\n\n## Examples\n\n```csharp\nvar colorSpace = SKColorSpace.CreateCicp(\n    SKColorspacePrimariesCicp.Rec2020,\n    SKColorspaceTransferFnCicp.Pq);\n```\n]]></format>",
        "remarksRequired": true,
        "summary": "Specifies the CICP (Coding-Independent Code Points) transfer function characteristics for a color space."
      },
      "docId": null,
      "memberType": "type"
    },
